| --------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| Vertical split        | <kbd>Alt+Shift++</kbd>                     |
| Horizontal split      | <kbd>Alt+Shift+-</kbd>                     |
| Auto split            | <kbd>Alt+Shift+d</kbd>                     |
| Switch between splits | <kbd>Alt</kbd> + arrow keys                |
